OL,3,CMore than 280,000 crimes unrecorded by
OL,4,Cpolice last year, watchdog finds
OL,6,FThe inspectorate said that forces
OL,7,Fshould improve recording of crimes
OL,8,Fsuch as harassment, stalking and
OL,9,Fcontrolling or coercive behaviour,
OL,10,Fthat disproportionately affect women
OL,11,Fand girls, and make up 37.9% of
OL,12,Funrecorded violent crime.
OL,14,FIt said they must also improve the
OL,15,Frecording of offences linked to
OL,16,Fdomestic abuse, crimes classed as anti-
OL,17,Fsocial behaviour, and crimes affecting
OL,18,Fvulnerable people.
