OL,6,F"However, there is still more to do.
OL,7,FThere remains much difference between
OL,8,Fforces in how well they record crime.
OL,10,F"For example, violent crimes still
OL,11,Faren't being recorded well enough and
OL,12,Fthe level of crime reporting related
OL,13,Fto antisocial behaviour remains
OL,14,Funacceptably low."
