OL,3,CMore than 280,000 crimes unrecorded by
OL,4,Cpolice last year, watchdog finds
OL,6,FThe report said: "This level of crime
OL,7,Frecording is unacceptably low, and it
OL,8,Fmeans victims remain at risk of harm."
OL,10,FFor violent crime, 93.6% of offences
OL,11,Fwere recorded, ranging between a top
OL,12,Frate of 98% for one force and less
OL,13,Fthan 90% for two forces.
OL,15,FInspectors said that officers should
OL,16,Fmake sure they properly record
OL,17,Funconfirmed reports of rape. Of the
OL,18,Fsamples reviewed between 2021 to 2025,
OL,19,Fthe correct procedure was used in less
OL,20,Fthan 70% of cases.
