OL,6,FOverall, between 2023 and 2025, police
OL,7,Frecorded 95.9% of sexual offences `
OL,8,Fthe highest rate was two forces that
OL,9,Frecorded 100% of such crimes in 2024,
OL,10,Fwhile the lowest was one that recorded
OL,11,F87% in 2023.
OL,13,FOver-recording was also an issue, with
OL,14,F2.3% of offences unnecessarily
OL,15,Fdocumented, with some forces
OL,16,Fmistakenly taking a "just in case"
OL,17,Fapproach, the report found.
